
Lua-Batteries on Parrot
=======================

This is the port of many libraries for Lua on Parrot
(http://github.com/fperrad/lua).

Build & Install
---------------

From source :
    $ parrot setup.pir
    $ parrot setup.pir test
    $ sudo parrot setup.pir install

Via Plumage :
    $ plumage install lua-batteries

Links
-----

The project is hosted at http://github.com/fperrad/lua-batteries/.

